<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">

<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - Rokt</title>
  <%- include ../partials/_head %>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include ../partials/_menu %>
    <main class="wrapper case-study rokt">
      <header class="case-header">
        <div class="case-header-content container">
          <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Rokt</h5>
          <h1 class="case-header-tagline">Solving the internet&rsquo;s&nbsp;
            <br />problem with ads</h1>
          <h6 class="case-header-type">Ecommerce Advertising Platform</h6>
        </div>
        <div class="case-header-content">
          <!-- <div class="frame frame-desktop edge-right darker shadow sr-right">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/header-screen.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div> -->
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="case-exec-summary padded">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="case-exec-summary-text">We helped Rokt wrangle its powerful algorithms and marketplace into a seamless suite, so that marketers, publishers
            and customers alike experience a better web.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="case-breakdown padded pink">
        <div class="container row">
          <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
            <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
            <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
              Teaching Marketing's&nbsp;
              <br />Old Dogs New Tricks
            </h3>
            <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
              A lot of experience, sophistication and nuance has gone into Rokt&rsquo;s history of serving content users actually care
              about. How can users efficiently understand a complex, new way of thinking?
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
            <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
            <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
              Ground the Data to&nbsp;
              <br />See the Signal
            </h3>
            <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
              We mapped a new mental model that aligns deep data concepts with the marketing objectives that users already know and use,
              amplified with Rokt&rsquo;s new brand and extended to places like tablet and mobile.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
            <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
            <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
              <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Research</li>
              <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
              <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Interaction Design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block extra-padded black rokt-hiw">
        <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">How it works</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block">
          <div class="container row">
            <div class="inner-box column gutter">
              <div class="frame frame-mobile lighter sr-stagger-tall">
                <div class="frame-container">
                  <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/step1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
                </div>
              </div>
              <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/step1-num.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute-top">
              <p class="case-block-text sr-stagger-bottom">
                A Publisher (like Ticketmaster) sells a ticket&nbsp;online.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="inner-box column gutter">
              <div class="frame frame-mobile lighter sr-stagger-tall">
                <div class="frame-container">
                  <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/step2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
                </div>
              </div>
              <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/step2-num.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute-top">
              <p class="case-block-text sr-stagger-bottom">
                Rokt finds a relevant Advertiser (like Uber) to show the customer an offered tailored to them, like a discounted ride to
                the concert.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="inner-box column gutter">
              <div class="frame frame-mobile lighter sr-stagger-tall">
                <div class="frame-container">
                  <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/step3.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
                </div>
              </div>
              <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/step3-num.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute-top">
              <p class="case-block-text sr-stagger-bottom">
                Instead of distracting ads in the middle of the shopping experience, customers get optional, always-relevant offers, meaning
                everybody wins.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block row padded offwhite">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content container gutter-right">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Getting the band&#32;
              <br />back together</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Advertisers run Campaigns on Publisher's checkout screens. They rely on each other, but previously had to use completely
              separate tools. Now, they can see the right amount of data 'across the fence,' in one platform.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column column-block gutter-left-mobile half-md">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop darker edge-right shadow sr-bottom lazy-ratio" data-width="1658" data-height="1640">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/dashboard.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block lazy-ratio" data-width="2000" data-height="690">
        <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/plot-graph.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
      </section>

      <section class="block row">
        <div class="inner-block padded absolute-center-md column half-md pink">
          <div class="inner-block-content container gutter-right">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Forests, not trees</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Creating a tangible, visual concept of abstract marketing goals was our top priority. Our cards keep users focused in a sea
              of data.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column column-block half-md hide-overflow light-pink">
          <div class="lazy-ratio full-height" data-width="1440" data-height="1576">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/graph1.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-top">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/graph2.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute contain sr-left">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/graph3.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute contain sr-bottom">
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block extra-padded offwhite">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="2608" data-height="264">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/placement.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image shadow contain sr-rotate">
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block row overflow black rokt-cards">
        <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center half-md">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="1648" data-height="2140">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/cards.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-reveal">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column order-top-xs half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content container">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Embarking on a journey</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              A complex script of dynamic steps is simplified in a single view, where users can quickly map out paths, measure performance,
              and keep up with customer behavior.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block extra-padded offwhite">
        <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Ready to go live</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              A strong emphasis on what-you-see-is-what-you get lets users actually see what their customers will see, in real time, so
              that every transaction is flawless.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block">
          <div class="container relative">
            <div class="frame frame-desktop darker shadow sr-tall lazy-ratio" data-width="2000" data-height="1127">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/onboarding.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
            </div>
          </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block padded rokt-market">
        <div class="container row">
          <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md">
            <div class="inner-block-content gutter-right">
              <h2 class="case-block-heading">A pulse on the&#32;
                <br />market from anywhere</h2>
              <p class="case-block-text">
                Customer opinions can shift rapidly; deals can go viral and sell out. We identified the most urgent features for our mobile
                interface, saving last-minute hikes to the office.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="inner-block column column-block half-md">
            <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="640" data-height="611">
              <div class="frame frame-mobile darker shadow absolute sr-stagger-bottom">
                <div class="frame-container">
                  <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/mobile-dashboard-main.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="frame frame-mobile darker shadow absolute sr-stagger-bottom">
                <div class="frame-container">
                  <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/mobile-dashboard-second.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block row">
        <div class="inner-block column column-block half-md hide-overflow light-pink">
          <div class="lazy-ratio full-height" data-width="1440" data-height="1348">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/rokt-meeting.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block order-top-xs padded absolute-center-md column half-md pink">
          <div class="inner-block-content container gutter-right">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Hearing it here first</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Users are more than just transactions. Brave traveled to Sydney and NYC for weeks of in-depth interviews with users of all
              kinds, learning the success and friction of customers, account managers, and support teams.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block extra-padded offwhite">
        <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">A roadmap to rock</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              We worked closely with the Rokt team to create a new UX guide that will help future teams learn and extend the new UX framework.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block">
          <div class="container relative">
            <div class="frame frame-desktop darker shadow sr-tall lazy-ratio" data-width="2000" data-height="1127">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/rokt/rokt-uxpl.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
            </div>
          </div>
      </section>

      <section class="case-referral row">
        <div class="inner-block padded column absolute-center-xs half-md pink">
          <div class="container">
            <p class="case-referral-blockquote">Long quote here from Rokt team member</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block padded column half-md black">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
            <p class="case-referral-text">Long quote here from Rokt team member lorem ipsum dolor sit amet. Long quote here from Gensler team member lorem
              ipsum. Long quote here from Gensler team member lorem ipsum.</p>
            <p class="case-referral-author">Firstname Last name,
              <em>Position, Rokt</em>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cta-block padded">
        <a href="./work/homezen" class="cta-button cta-button-left" title="Previous Case">Previous Case</a>
        <div class="cta-content container">
          <div class="cta-text">Sometimes, you find something that just works.</div>
          <a href="/approach" class="btn btn-text icon-arrow">See Our Approach</a>
        </div>
        <a href="./work/felix" class="cta-button cta-button-right" title="Next Case">Next Case</a>
      </section>
      <%- include ../partials/_footer %>
    </main>

    <%- include ../partials/_footer-scripts %>

</body>

</html>